cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.GT 

This paper proposes a novel hierarchical reinforcement learning model for learning fairness in multi-agent systems. The paper focuses on the optimization of joint policies for multiple agents, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), control systems (cs.SY), and game theory (cs.GT). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
